## §2. 5-axis cross-contribution

- **Q (QUANTUM)**: cyclic peptide conformational sampling VQE — backbone macrocyclic ring 의 ring-flipping & cis/trans proline isomer ensemble 양자 sampling natural fit; macrocycle binding mode (chameleonic conformation — exposed polar in water, masked polar in membrane) ΔΔG calculation; PAMPA / Caco-2 permeability prediction (polar surface area + intramolecular H-bond shielding) quantum-chemical refinement; "beyond rule-of-5" descriptor 의 양자 모델링.
- **W (WEAVE)**: peptide stapling scaffold — primary fit. Hydrocarbon i,i+4 / i,i+7 olefin metathesis staple (Grubbs RCM); lactam bridge (Lys-Glu); disulfide cyclization; thioether (Cys-bromoacetyl); head-to-tail amide cyclization; click triazole; β-hairpin / α-helix template; PEG linker 등 cyclization linker chemistry 가 W-axis 핵심 paradigm.
- **V (VIROCAPSID)**: peptide AAV gene therapy 비-fit (peptide 는 non-genetic modality); 단 venom-derived peptide gene cassette → AAV in-vivo expression (e.g., ziconotide-like conotoxin AAV intrathecal) niche 가능; capsid display peptide ligand (cell-targeting peptide, RGD/CendR) 는 AAV engineering 에 cross-link.
- **RB (RIBOZYME / RNA)**: peptide mRNA in-vivo expression — secreted peptide (GLP-1, insulin) mRNA-LNP cassette; mRNA display library 자체가 RNA-peptide covalent fusion (puromycin linker) → RNA-peptide co-evolution paradigm; aptamer-peptide bispecific (SOMAmer); ribosome stalling cyclic peptide biosynthesis (RiPP — lanthipeptide, lasso peptide) RB-natural-product overlap.
- **NB (NANOBOT)**: peptide nano-delivery — oral nano formulation (semaglutide SNAC absorption enhancer paradigm); LNP-encapsulated peptide; peptide-drug conjugate (PDC, e.g., 177Lu-DOTATATE Lutathera); cell-penetrating peptide (CPP — TAT, R8, penetratin); enzyme-responsive nano-release; peptide self-assembly nanofiber (β-sheet, coiled-coil) — peptide ↔ NB bidirectional cross-link.

