## §4. Phase α–ε — hxq-peptide-glp1-001 candidate

- **Phase α (concept lock, cycle 1)**: triple GLP-1/GIP/glucagon agonist + oral bioavailable cyclic peptide candidate; retatrutide-class 3-incretin pharmacology + Rybelsus-class SNAC oral absorption + macrocyclization (head-to-tail) for protease resistance.
- **Phase β (in-silico, cycle 2-3)**: VQE backbone conformational ensemble (Q-axis); stapling vs head-to-tail vs lactam comparative SAR (W-axis); permeability + protease t½ + GLP-1R/GIPR/GcgR triple-receptor docking ΔΔG; oral PK simulation (rat-to-human allometric).
- **Phase γ (synthesis + in-vitro, cycle 3-4)**: SPPS (Fmoc) + on-resin macrocyclization; cAMP assay (3 receptors); plasma stability; PAMPA + Caco-2; rat oral PK pilot.
- **Phase δ (in-vivo, cycle 4-5)**: DIO mouse weight loss (vs tirzepatide head-to-head); ZDF rat HbA1c; cynomolgus oral PK + tolerability; MASH STAM model liver fibrosis.
- **Phase ε (clinical translation, cycle 5+)**: IND-enabling tox; Phase 1 SAD/MAD healthy + T2DM; Phase 2 obesity (BMI ≥30); 잠재 KOL site 한국 (서울대/세브란스/아산) — K-pharma peptide 진입 leverage.

## §5. raw#10 honest C3 — peptide / macrocycle paradigm

**Historical paradigm arc**: 1922 insulin (Banting–Best, 첫 peptide drug, 100+ year therapeutic mainstay) → 1953 oxytocin synthesis (du Vigneaud Nobel) → 1980s cyclosporine (Sandoz, fungal cyclic peptide, transplant 혁명) + tacrolimus/sirolimus (Streptomyces macrolide) → 1998 thalidomide re-approval (cross-link molecular glue) → 2005 exenatide (Gila monster venom-derived 첫 GLP-1 → "venom-to-drug" paradigm 점화) → 2004 ziconotide (cone snail conotoxin, intrathecal chronic pain) → 2010s liraglutide/semaglutide (Novo Nordisk obesity 시장 폭발) → 2019 oral semaglutide (Rybelsus, SNAC absorption enhancer 로 oral peptide barrier 돌파) → 2022 tirzepatide (dual incretin, blockbuster $20B+ trajectory) → 2024 OSA expansion (tirzepatide SURMOUNT-OSA) → 2025+ retatrutide triple agonist Phase 3 + orforglipron oral non-peptide GLP-1.

**Drug-like properties challenges**: peptide modality 의 3대 장벽 — (1) **oral bioavailability** (<1% native, SNAC enhancer + PEGylation + macrocyclization 으로 ~1-5% 도달); (2) **membrane permeability** (>500 Da + polar surface area >140 Å² → "beyond rule-of-5" zone, chameleonic conformation 으로 우회); (3) **protease resistance** (trypsin/chymotrypsin/DPP-4 t½ minutes → cyclization + N-methylation + D-amino acid + fatty acid acylation 으로 반감기 일/주 단위 연장). Cyclosporine 이 이 3대 장벽 모두 native 통과한 "natural rule-breaker" — macrocyclic + N-methyl ×7 + chameleonic. Tirzepatide 는 fatty acid acylation (C20 di-acid) + albumin binding 으로 once-weekly.

**한국 K-pharma peptide 진입**: 한미약품 **LAPSCOVERY** platform (long-acting protein conjugate, efpeglenatide GLP-1 / Rolontis G-CSF); 동아ST + **ABL Bio** peptide-based bispecific 및 BBB shuttle; SK biopharm peptide pipeline; 종근당/녹십자 biosimilar peptide; 에스티팜 peptide CDMO (oligonucleotide + peptide dual capability) — K-pharma peptide ecosystem 이 mAb 보다 빠른 진입 가능 (CMC barrier 낮음, SPPS 합성 기반 globally competitive).

**양자–VQE의 cyclic peptide conformational sampling fit**: cyclic peptide 는 backbone ring 의 conformational ensemble (cis/trans proline, ring puckering, intramolecular H-bond network) 가 binding 과 permeability 동시 결정 — classical MD 로는 ms-timescale 충분 sampling 어려움 (ergodicity 문제). VQE / quantum imaginary-time evolution 으로 Boltzmann-weighted ensemble 직접 sampling → "chameleonic descriptor" (water-vs-membrane ΔΔG) 정확도 향상. 이것이 Q-axis 의 peptide platform 핵심 niche — small molecule (rigid) 도, biologics (large/solvent-exposed) 도 아닌 macrocycle 의 conformational complexity 가 양자 alg fit.

**Future direction**: (1) **oral peptide expansion** — semaglutide oral 성공 후 oral GLP-1 (orforglipron non-peptide), oral PCSK9, oral PTH 등 platform 확장; (2) **cyclic PROTAC** — macrocyclic ternary stabilizer, cooperativity α factor 향상 (cross-link platform_molecular_glue); (3) **mRNA display library** — RaPID system (Suga, Tokyo Univ) + PeptiDream 으로 trillion-scale macrocycle library 탐색; (4) **venom-derived discovery 2.0** — AI 기반 conotoxin/scorpion toxin proteome mining (cross-link platform_bio_evolution); (5) **stapled peptide α-helix mimetic** — undruggable PPI (MDM2-p53, β-catenin-TCF) 표적; (6) **GLP-1 next-gen** — quad agonist (GLP-1/GIP/glucagon/amylin), CNS-penetrant for Alzheimer (semaglutide EVOKE Phase 3 AD trial).

